extDescription.message: Save and restore the state of windows and tabs. It also supports automatic saving.

searchBarPlaceholder.message: Meklēt pēc sesijas vai cilnes nosaukuma

letsSaveLabel.message: Let's save the session by clicking the lower right button.

openInCurrentWindowCaptionLabel.message: Open the session in the current window. Inactive windows and all tabs are closed.

addToCurrentWindowCaptionLabel.message: Add tabs to the current window. If the session contains multiple windows, open it in the new window.

makeCopySessionLabel.message: Make a copy of the session

indexedDBErrorLabel.message: IndexedDB is not available in your browser.

ifOpenNewWindowCaptionLabel.message: If unchecked, the session overwrites the current window.

ifLazyLoadingCaptionLabel.message:
When opening a session, the contents of each page are not loaded until you select the tab.
If unchecked, memory usage greatly increases when session is restored.

isUseDiscardedLabel.message: Use the "discarded" property for lazy loading

isUseDiscardedCaptionLabel.message: Enabling this option will improve performance when opening tabs.

isUseDiscardedCaption2Label.message: The favicon of the lazy loading tab is not displayed.

isRestoreWindowPositionCaptionLabel.message: Restore window's position and size when opening session.

openPreviousSessionCaptionLabel.message: Atvērt sesiju, kas tika aizvērta pēdējo reizi.

openStartupSessionCaptionLabel.message: Open the sessions registered for startup. You can register for startup from the menu in the session list.

shouldTrackNewWindowCaptionLabel.message: When a new window is opened within a tracking session, include it in the tracking.

ifAutoSaveCaptionLabel.message: Saglabāt sesiju ik pēc X minūtēm.

autoSaveLimitCaptionLabel.message: Maximum number of saved sessions (in this way).

ifAutoSaveWhenCloseLabel.message: Save the session when window was closed

ifAutoSaveWhenCloseCaptionLabel.message: Save the session that includes only one closed window.

autoSaveWhenCloseCaptionLabel.message: Maximum number of saved sessions (in this way).

ifAutoSaveWhenExitBrowserCaptionLabel.message: Save the session that includes multiple windows that was closed in a row.

autoSaveWhenExitBrowserCaptionLabel.message: Maximum number of saved sessions (in this way).

useTabTitleforAutoSaveLabel.message: Izmantot lapas nosaukumu automātiski saglabātu sesijas nosaukumos

useTabTitleforAutoSaveCaptionLabel.message: Saglabājot sesiju automātiski, izmantot atvērtās lapas nosaukumu kā sesijas nosaukumu.

ifBackupCaptionLabel.message: When browser starts up, create a backup file of sessions and save it in the download folder.

individualBackupCaptionLabel.message:
Each session is saved in an individual file.
If unchecked, all sessions will be saved as a single file, which may overwhelm your storage space.

backupFolderCaptionLabel.message: Specify the folder to save the backup file. The save location is limited to the folder under browser download folder.

backupFilesLimitCaptionLabel.message: Ja rezerves kopiju failu skaits pārsniedz šo vērtību, tie tiek dzēsti augošā secībā vispirms vecākais.

ignoreUrlListLabel.message: URL list to ignore when saving session

ignoreUrlListCaptionLabel.message: If the tab URL matches the list, it will not be recorded in the session. The list allows "*" wildcards.

shouldSaveDeviceNameCaptionLabel.message: Add the device name as a tag when saving a session. When using cloud sync, you can distinguish it from sessions on other devices.

applyDeviceNameCaptionLabel.message: Pievienot ierīces nosaukumu visām saglabātajām sesijām.

applyDeviceNameConfirmLabel.message: Vai lietot ierīces nosaukumu visām sesijām?

compressFaviconUrlCaptionLabel.message: Saspiest favicon ikonas, kas saglabā sesiju.

compressAllSessionsCaptionLabel.message: Compress the favicons of all currently saved sessions. This will save memory usage and speed up session loading.

ifSavePrivateWindowCaptionLabel.message: If unchecked, ignores the private window when saving the session.

ifSupportTstCaptionLabel.message:
Restore tree state of Tree Style Tab.
When this option is enabled, it takes time to restore the session.

saveTabGroupsCaptionLabel.message: Save and restore the state of tab groups. To enable this feature, you need to install the following extension.

tstDelayCaptionLabel.message: To restore the state of the tree, wait time is required to open the tab. Increase this value if the tree is not restored correctly.

truncateTitleLabel.message: Display session name within one line

truncateTitleCaptionLabel.message: If the session name in the session list extends over more than one line, it is truncated on one line and displayed.

enabledCloudSyncCaptionLabel.message: Save sessions to Google Drive™ and sync with other computers.

signInRequiredLabel.message: Requires sign in for cloud sync.

enabledAutoSyncCaptionLabel.message: Execute cloud sync when the browser is launched and when the session is saved.

includesAutoSaveToSyncCaptionLabel.message: Upload / download auto save sessions in cloud sync.

isShowOpenButtonsLabel.message: Display open / delete buttons in session list

isShowOpenButtonsCaptionLabel.message: Display open / delete buttons when the cursor is over the session list.

isSessionListOpenInTabCaptionLabel.message: Open session list in tab when button on toolbar is clicked.

isShowOptionsPageWhenUpdatedCaptionLabel.message: Display the options page when Tab Session Manager is updated. You can know the update contents quickly.

isDebugModeCaptionLabel.message: When debug mode is enabled, the log is output to the debugger.

exportSettingsCaptionLabel.message: Save the settings as a json file on the computer.

importSettingsCaptionLabel.message: Load the settings file saved on the computer.

resetSettingsCaptionLabel.message: Atjaunojiet visus iestatījumus uz noklusējuma vērtībām.

importCaptionLabel.message: Ielādēt datorā saglabātās sesijas un pievienot tās sesiju sarakstam.

importCaptionLabel3.message: How to import sessions from other extensions

urlImportCaptionLabel.message:
Create a session from list of URLs and add it to the session list.
Format: <URL> <page title (optionally)>

includeModifierKeysMessage.message: Iekļaujiet vai nu Ctrl, vai Alt taustiņu

includeMacModifierKeysMessage.message: Iekļaujiet vai nu Command, Ctrl vai nu Alt taustiņu

donationCaptionLabel.message:
Paldies, ka izmantojat Tab Session Manager.
Jūsu atbalsts būs liels iedrošinājums, lai es turpinātu uzlabot papildinājumu.
Ja jums patīk un izmantojat Tab Session Manager ikdienā, es priecātos, ja jūs apsvērtu iespēju ziedot.

warningRemoveAllMessage.message: Dzēst visas sesijas. Vai esat pārliecināti?

replacedPageMessage.message: Šo lapu nevar atvērt izmantojot Tab Session Manager.
